data.description: Nestled within the esteemed Avon Grove School District, this charming 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom home offers a perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Boasting spacious bedrooms, an inviting eat-in kitchen with modern appliances, and a convenient one-car garage, this residence is designed for easy living. Step outside to discover a delightful fire pit patio, perfect for cozy gatherings under the stars. With its desirable location and appealing amenities, this home is a must-see for those seeking the ideal blend of suburban tranquility and modern comfort with a new roof to boot. Schedule your showing today and make this delightful house your new home!
